Author: saturn.network
Title: [ANN][ETH][ETC]Saturn Network - Cross Chain Uncensorable Decentralized Exchange
Body: Bump!    What is Saturn Network?  Saturn Network is a decentralized exchange for trading ERC20 or ERC223 tokens, it is being developed to be cross-chain and is currently live on Ethereum Classic. We will soon be launching on Ethereum and then will target a third blockchain such as EOS, TRON, NEO or EOS. Saturn Network has a unique implementation as it is truly decentralized and has an orderbook which is completely on chain which is uncensorable. Trading on Saturn Network is quick and effortless, as there is no need to fill in a KYC or set up an account: all trading happens wallet to wallet in one transaction so you never have to face problems with deposits or withdrawals because you never give up control of your funds.  Just watch how easy it is to set up Buy or Sell orders and share your individual order links in this demonstration:    Key Features (Click on the image to go to our blog and learn more)  1. Decentralized Loyalty Program: All your paid trading fees are reimbursed with SATURN tokens.    2. Exchange profits are shared and distributed to token holders.    3. Automated Token Self-Listing, every token can be listed on our exchange and we will never de-list anything as we do not believe in censorship.    4. Decentralized, peer to peer trading, every trade happens wallet to wallet in one transaction.    5. Full mobile support via Trust Wallet App.    6. Individual & shareable order links.    We are actively developing our exchange so please if you have any suggestions for features or feedback, please come drop by our community forum and let us know!  https://forum.saturn.network  #TeamSaturn Future is bright!

Author: saturn.network
Title: [ANN][ETH][ETC]Saturn Network - Cross Chain Uncensorable Decentralized Exchange
Body: What is Saturn Token?  Saturn Network is a protocol that allows access to a decentralized order book in just one transaction. Allowing decentralized exchanges to share a liquidity pool and feel the benefits of a much higher trading volume. It requires no deposits and runs completely on the blockchain, making it always accessible to everyone. Furthermore, it has been built with shared ownership in mind to ensure there are no imbalances of power: holding SATURN tokens means you are part of the Saturn DAO.  Saturn DAO (Decentralized Autonomous Organisation) ensures our protocol is built for the people and governed by the people. We have chosen this path because it corrects any imbalance of power that developers or exchange owners have over a project. Once you buy SATURN tokens you will become an essential part of our development team. Changes to the protocol can only be made if you vote for them to happen with your tokens.    You can learn more about Saturn DAO in the following blog article:    The voting will be done via blockchain and enforced in the form of a smart contract. This means our protocol is 100% transparent and uncensorable, and once launched on the blockchain it can never be stopped or taken down. Your vote matters!  Scenarios of token use:  ● Change the default Exchange Fees. ● Payout Dividends (collected fees) to SATURN holders. ● Decentralized Loyalty Program (Exchange Mining).  We are currently discussing how the voting should happen & what Saturn DAO members will be able to vote on, please come and join in here.  To remain completely decentralized every chain that Saturn Protocol supports will have its own Saturn DAO and therefore its own Saturn tokens. Currently, we have a token on Ethereum & Ethereum Classic.  Saturn DAO Token details   ● Platform: Ethereum ● Standard: ERC223 ● Symbol: SATURN ● Contract: 0xb9440022a095343b440d590fcd2d7a3794bd76c8 ● Decimals: 4 ● Total supply: 1,000,000,000   Saturn Classic DAO Token details   ● Platform: Ethereum Classic ● Standard: ERC223 ● Symbol: SATURN ● Contract: 0xAC55641Cbb734bdf6510d1bBd62E240c2409040f ● Decimals: 4 ● Total supply: 1,000,000,000   What is Saturn Network?  Saturn Network is a decentralized exchange for trading ERC20 or ERC223 tokens, it is being developed to be cross-chain and is currently live on Ethereum Classic. We will soon be launching on Ethereum and then will target a third blockchain such as EOS, TRON, NEO or EOS. Saturn Network has a unique implementation as it is truly decentralized and has an orderbook which is completely on chain which is uncensorable. Trading on Saturn Network is quick and effortless, as there is no need to fill in a KYC or set up an account: all trading happens wallet to wallet in one transaction so you never have to face problems with deposits or withdrawals because you never give up control of your funds.  Just watch how easy it is to set up Buy or Sell orders and share your individual order links in this demonstration:    Key Features (Click on the image to go to our blog and learn more)  1. Automated Token Self-Listing, every token can be listed on our exchange and we will never de-list anything as we do not believe in censorship.    4. Decentralized, peer to peer trading, every trade happens wallet to wallet in one transaction.    5. Full mobile support via Trust Wallet App.    6. Individual & shareable order links.    We are actively developing our exchange so please if you have any suggestions for features or feedback, please come drop by our community forum and let us know!  https://forum.saturn.network  #TeamSaturn Future is bright!
